==================
RAPLEAF DIRECT API
==================

For general information regarding the personalization API, visit http://www.rapleaf.com/developers/api_docs/personalization/direct. The personalization API's terms and conditions are stated at http://www.rapleaf.com/developers/api_usage.

The API is queried by calling the queryByEmail function belonging to the RapleafApi file. An example script, RapleafExample, is provided. The example script queries Rapleaf's database for an e-mail given to RapleafApi's constructor.